Dialogs.Dialog: 高嶺
Hey, there's a song called "Hato Poppo".
Oh, I sang it when I was in kindergarten.
That song... "If you want it", it's a little arrogant. I feel like I'm looking down on you.
... Do you look down on a pigeon?
How would you feel if you were a pigeon? Try to feel like a pigeon.
Feeling like a pigeon... Po... Popopo.
Well then, it's just a cry. It's not like that anymore, just try to make yourself feel good.
Pigeon feeling... I'll think about it.
It's about our talk of the pigeon from last time.
高嶺
Yeah, did you think about it?
I think it's a problem for pigeons, too. They say "I'm going to do it", and they eat.
You mean pigeons are bad?
I wonder if pigeons need to change their mindset.
What is a change of consciousness of pigeons?
If you say from above, you have to eat beans. That kind of resolute attitude...
But I think if I have something I like in front of me, I will eat it as my instict.
If you have something you like in front of you...
What's wrong? So suddenly...
高嶺
I thought about it, but the song "Hato Poppo"...
Oh, did you come up with a way to make pigeons change their minds?
Why not change the lyrics instead?
Huh, who's that?
How are you? If you want beans, I'll give you♪
... Hey, I think it's a little bad.
As for the view of the world and the composition... What do you think?
That's right. It may be good to change "I'll give you" to "Can you eat with me?"...
Are you going to eat with the pigeon?
Yes, yes. Not only pigeons, but also human beings change their consciousness.
Fufu, we too?
高嶺
I thought about it... The song "Hato Poppo".
I was still thinking.
I don't think it's because I've called pigeon-san away.
"Pigeon-san"?
Right. So I was thinking about new lyrics...
Well, I thought the other day, but I can't change old masterpieces without permission.
But, the feelings of a pigeon... Speaking of which, what do you think about it?
For that... I'm going to ask the pigeon directly.
Can you listen to them?
I'll listen when I go to the park on a date. If there was a pigeon there...
Fufu, really?
高嶺
... Hey, what do you do when you can't sleep at night?
I think about ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Take it seriously!
I'm serious, really. I think about ▲高嶺＊＊▲, and go to bed.
My... Can you sleep when you think about me?
Don't sleep. I don't know what to say, but I'm so happy and mentally calm.
I'm not sure, but if you think about me, you can sleep... Does it work for Ako-chan?
Ako-chan?
My cousing. She consulted me about her lack of sleep... I... I'll say that she must think of me.
Wait, wait a second.
Why?
高嶺
Ako-chan, she can't sleep well yet...
Is that your cousin?
Right. We live a bit apart but we're the same age.
Huh, I'm sure your cousin ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is a beautiful woman.
She's much more beautiful than me.
That's not true.
... You've never met Ako-chan? I don't think you know her face or style.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, there's no way she's more beautiful than you.
... Yes, there are. People more beautiful than me... There are many.
Not here. At least not in my world.
... A strange world.
高嶺
Ako-chan asked my again...
You cousin with insomnia?
It's not insomnia, it's just that she can't sleep easily... Is there a good solution?
Why doesn't she go to the batting center before going to bed and use a lot of physical strength?
She's a girls, so that kind of thing...
For example counting up to 50,000 sheep.
It seems she counted sheep many times...
It's like relaxing your body and mind, as if there weren't any food.
But eating something before going to bed is not good for you.
It's just a light meal... I don't know what to do.
Hmm...
高嶺
Ako-chan said she could sleep with a lettuce.
Oh, I'm glad... What, lettuce? You can sleep if you eat lettuce, or did ▲高嶺＊＊▲ created it?
Not me, it reminds me about the British rabbit picture book, and yes, lettuce.
... I don't really understand the story.
In the picture book, the rabbits always sleep when they eat lettuce. I remembered that.
... Was Ako-chan a rabbit?
Fufu, she's human. But maybe I look like a little rabbit. When I tried to eat it, I became sleepy...
Really? I wonder if it would work for me, but there are times when I can't sleep after 5 minutes.
It's a good enough time. And, you're not a little rabbit... A capybara, maybe?
Me? A capybara? Why such a maniac animal... Do I look like that?
Ufufu, what's with your face right now? Thank you for taking the hint.
高嶺
Hey, what would you like if you had an animal?
I can't keep pets in my room...
Then, what if you could keep one?
...Honestly, it would be a goldfish or a turtle. They don't take up much space and are easy to take care.
For turtles, rabbits are better.
"Rabbit and turtle". It doesn't sound good.
Then a rabbit! If you want to keep one, rabbits are the right choice, right?
You're talking about "ifs", are you?
高嶺
Hey, if you could keep a rabbit, what kind of breed would you like?
Breed... Are there so many kinds of rabbits?
The Netherlands Dwarf, Lopyear, Angola...
...The normal one it's fine. The white one that appears in fairy tales.
Japanese White.
That's fine, white rabbits are cute.
Say it again.
It's okay. Why?
Not that one, the other one.
"White rabbits are cute".
Fufu♪ Right?
高嶺
Hey, if you keep a rabbit...
The topic comes ofter, but I can't really keep one.
Someday you will keep one. It doesn't have to be immediately.
Someday...
You don't like it?
It's not that I don't like it, but the room must be larger.
It's all right.
I'm not there during the day, so I don't mind that kind of thing.
It's okay, I'll be waiting for you to come back.
You're very confident.
I'm a rabbit, so it's okay.
As I said before, talking about keeping something, a dog isn't an option.
高嶺
No good.
... A cat?
I said rabbit. No words for boys.
Well, a rabbit is okay...
If we live together, it has to be a rabbit.
You really like rabbits. If I want to keep one, it's just a story.
That's a little different.
You guys, that's it.
? Me, I live alone?
Right now, right? I'm talking about having a family in the future.
高嶺
The other day, an emergency patient came...
Huh.▲高嶺＊＊▲, is your house an emergency designated hospital?
It's not, but you can't refuse the person who came. He was an ojisan who was brought to my family.
Why didn't you call an ambulance?
He said he doesn't like ambulances. Because it's a bother to other people.
But in your house▲高嶺＊＊▲ might have been annoying.
It's an important patient. It's natural for Papa to see people.
Yeah, that's fine. So, what about the old man?
We went to the emergency center by ambulance. It was a dangerous place, but after that it was safe.
He got in one after all. If he's saved, that's fine.
高嶺
The ojisan who was sick last time, was admitted to the university hospital.
He doesn't like ambulances.
I was hard to persuade him to get on.
He was stubborn.
So, I got a phone call from the hospital to thank me...
I wish he could be fine enough to call you.
I wonder if he used the hospital phone. Papa said he couldn't walk because of those symptoms.
It may have been impossible. A stubborn person has a strong sense of duty.
I wonder if that doesn't make his symptoms worse...
There are a lot of people who can use their phones in the hospital now, maybe he went to bed properly?
I wonder if the ojisan can use his cell phone...
（Certainly some people are not good at being young... ▲高嶺＊＊▲）
高嶺
The ojisan called to thank me.
Ah, he's still in the hospital?
He's been able to walk, but he's still leaving the hospital.
I see. Why doesn't him stay?
Papa. Because he doesn't receive anything except medical treatment fees.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ you father is not stubborn... he's a straight person.
Fufu, he is stubborn.
Yes... But it seems like a lot of trouble if my girlfriend's father is stubborn.
Is that so? Why?
Like... "Give me your daughter's hand please" and he says "I'm not going to do it".
... Oh you.
高嶺
The ojisan who was in the hospital said he could leave the hospital soon.
Then,▲高嶺＊＊▲make sure he doesn't forget to bring a thank-you gift to your house.
But, I'm sure Papa won't take it.
Hmm.
It would be rude to return an item you received.
If you park an ambulance that you don't like in front of your house, the ojisan won't get in.
Ambulances can't be used for that.
Then ask your father to dress as an ambulance.
It's impossible... Fufu, Papa's an ambulance?
Yes. With this... cardboard or something.
Fufu, fufufu. I'm sorry, Papa... It's funny.
高嶺
There is a story about the king of donkey ears.
Oh, yeah.
Huh, I wonder who did you find you were a donkey with only your ears.
...Ah, if it's just the ears, it's hard to tell whether it's a donkey, a horse, or a dog.
If you're a pig, you can tell them apart.
I'm sorry, but pig's ears would make me be eaten.I'm sure it's going to be a strange story.
Pig's ear... do you eat them?
Mimigar is Okinawan food made of pig's ear. I've eaten it before.
I ate it... But this story isn't about Okinawa, is it?
I mean, it's a country that doesn't see donkey ears as edible. Where is it?
Every country is the same... Surely.
It's about the donkey ear's story. It's easy to understand if they are rabbit's ears.
高嶺
It jumps out and I can't hide it.
But I think it would be popular. Bunny King! There is a bunny girl next to me.
...What? You're staring at me suddenly.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, the rabbit ears would look good.
Me... a bunny girls next to the king?
I'm sure it will look good on you. Yes, it definitely suits you.
I don't want that... But, it would be good if you were the king.
（King, that's hard）
高嶺
Hey you. You work part- time, correct?
Hmm.
Me too... i think I'll give it a try.
Why? Not enough pocket money.
No, that's not why... Social studies, I guess?
So that's it.
And you...
Me?
For studying at school, club activities, and part-time jobs... I want to be an apprentice.
（I wonder is she's seriously want to learn from me...）
By the way, what happened to the part-time job?
高嶺
Yes... I talked with Mama and Papa...
Oh, I wonder what they told you.
Papa said "High school students should concentrate on their studies and club activities".
I see... But that's fine, isn't it?
Why?
▲高嶺＊＊▲if you work part- time, we would spend less time together.
I see, but...
No good. In high school, concentrate on your studies and club activities.
Geez... I get it, Papa.
高嶺
Hey, how do you put backspin on your serve?
I can't!
Why? Rina-senpai said there was a person who was doing it.
Rina-senpai is ranked in the district... Serve and backspin?
How do you do it?
If it's an overserver, you can't backspin, it's under it, isn't it?
Isn't that a slice?
It's not a slice server. At this angle... this way...
Without a racket, I don't know.
That's why it's like this. This way!
Are you okay?
It's nothing.
高嶺
Sometimes my backhand and top spin don't come right...
Oh, then it's non-spining. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, you have a lot of two-handed hits, right?
I'm better at using both hands because I hit it by rotating my body.
If you lower your racket's head when you hit it back, you'll naturally get a topspin.
It's easier said than done.
It's like this... All you have to do is take it back and return it like this.
If you don't have a racket, you won't even know the head.
Look at my wrist, pull like this... Like this!
Are you okay?
A little... I just slipped.
Fufu, don't overdo it okay?
高嶺
...What?
No, nothing.
... That so.
You're watching, aren't you?
You can see it, no?
I don't hate, but...
Then it's good, right?
高嶺
I'm watching again.
Fufu, I want to see it.
Why? It's not really funny.
No, it's fun, isn't it?
... I don't have fun looking at the mirror.
I wonder if that's the problem.
Oh, but it might be fun to see ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s face.
... I don't enjoy looking in the mirror, do I?
That's not the problem... Huh?
Fufu, isn't it fun?
（Oh, well）
